Ecole Notre Dame de la Providence de Karubanda,ni ishuri ry'isumbuye ryibanda byumwihariko ku burezi bw'umwana w'umukobwa.

== '''Amateka''' ==
Iri shuri ryatangiye mu mwaka w'1957<nowiki/>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/10104, rishinzwe n'ababikira basabira  roho zo muri pirigatori (Les soiers auxilliatrices plus les Ã¢mes du purugatoire). Mu gutangira kwaryo,ryari rije kwita ku burezi bw'umwana w'umukobwa, rikaba ryari riherereyebahazwi ubu nk'akarere ka Gisagara. Abana babakobwa baturukuga mu Rwanda n' iburundi ariho baje kwiga bitewe nuko muri icyo gihe uburezi bw'umunwana w'umukobwa ntabwo bwari bufite agaciro. Ku bijyanye nibyahigirwaga rero,habaga  amasomo yibijyanye n'indimi, imirimo y'intoki,ubuzima bwo mu mutwe(psychology),ndetse nimyafatire y'abantu  (sociology).  

Mu mwaka w'1999,nibwo iri shuri ryahinduye izina,aho ryitwaga Ecole Sociale, rigahinduka Ecole Notre Dames de la providence de Karubanda. 

== '''Aho riherereye''' ==
Ecole Notre Dame de la Providence de Karubanda iherereye mu karere ka huye,umurenge wa Ngoma, kuri metero 100 uvuye kuri garre nkuru ya huye.

